Notes: SP's Schultz hit runner in lane with 45 seconds left and SP missed shot at
buzzer as game went to OT...Game was tied 21 times and largest lead was five
points - the most recent being 23-18 UWO with 10:31 left in first half...SP's
Kraemer made layup with 54 seconds left in OT to break 73-73 tie.
Game.Officials: Lou Eisenman,  Barb Fagan & Dennis Inderdahl
